attributeList.attribute: Role in the early stages of the homologous recombination DNA damage repair process. Recruits the Rad55-Rad57 complex (CPX-3139) and the homologous recombination machinery to the sites of single-stranded DNA gaps left by replication-blocking lesions to complete error-free DNA-damage tolerance.
The Shu complex takes the shape of a boomerang with DNA filaments probably attaching to the bottom of the concave.
